ZH: 贸易是国际经济关系中最重要的环节之一。
EN: Trade is one of the most important components of international economic relations.

ZH: 这个国家有着丰富的贸易资源。
EN: This country has abundant trade resources.

ZH: 贸易战可能会对全球经济造成负面影响。
EN: A trade war may have a negative impact on the global economy.

ZH: 这份贸易协议将为两国带来更多合作机会。
EN: This trade agreement will bring more opportunities for cooperation between the two countries.

ZH: 欧盟是世界上最大的贸易伙伴之一。
EN: The EU is one of the largest trade partners in the world.

ZH: 贸易顺差可以为一个国家带来经济增长。
EN: A trade surplus can bring economic growth to a country.

ZH: 这家公司从事国际贸易业务。
EN: This company is engaged in international trade.

ZH: 贸易制裁可能会对经济产生重大影响。
EN: Trade sanctions may have a significant impact on the economy.

ZH: 他们的主要收入来源于国际贸易。
EN: Their main source of income comes from international trade.

ZH: 这个港口每天都有大量的贸易活动。
EN: There is a lot of trade activity at this port every day.

ZH: 有些国家在国际贸易中起着重要作用。
EN: Some countries play important roles in international trade.

ZH: 贸易保护主义正在逐渐升温。
EN: Trade protectionism is gradually increasing.

ZH: 这个行业的发展受到了贸易摩擦的影响。
EN: The development of this industry is affected by trade frictions.

ZH: 对贸易逆差的压力越来越大。
EN: The pressure on trade deficits is increasing.

ZH: 需要加强贸易合作，实现互利共赢。
EN: It is necessary to strengthen trade cooperation and achieve mutual benefit.

ZH: 通过贸易往来，各国之间的关系得到了深化。
EN: Relations between countries have deepened through trade exchanges.

ZH: 贸易的发展促进了全球化的进程。
EN: The development of trade promotes the process of globalization.

ZH: 贸易自由化是国际经贸交流的重要方向之一。
EN: Trade liberalization is one of the important directions in international economic and trade exchanges.

ZH: 战争会对贸易造成不利影响。
EN: Wars will have adverse effects on trade.

ZH: 政府应该促进贸易便利化。
EN: Governments should promote trade facilitation.
